what_worked: Applied dimension_cte_isolate, multi_dimension_prefetch: Isolated the complex OR conditions into a pre-filtered CTE that extracts distinct manufacturers meeting the criteria, then used a simple IN join instead of a correlated subquery. This allows DuckDB to push predicates early and avoid repeated full table scans.
why_it_worked: Pre-filtering all dimension tables into CTEs avoids repeated full-table scans; Pre-filtering multiple dimension tables in parallel reduces join fan-out
